Thanks [~suma.shivaprasad], 

Overall the fix looks good.
Not related to the patch, but one existing logic need to be updated. 
{code}
  public Resource getResourcePreempted() {
    try {
      readLock.lock();
      return resourcePreempted;
    } finally {
      readLock.unlock();
    }
  }
{code}
Instead of doing this, we should return resourcePreempted.clone() so the consumer can get a copy of the resource.
